definition.value: A C4-dicarboxylate resulting from the removal of a proton from both carboxylic acid groups of methylmalonic acid.
A UDP-rhamnose in which the rhamnose component has L-configuration.
The meso-diastereomer of 1,4-dimercaptobutane-2,3-diol; a sulfur-containing sugar derived from the monosaccharide erythrose; and an epimer of dithiothreitol.
